<content title="Calvary Austin Internet Ministry Vision" base=".">
  <heading>Internet Ministry Vision</heading>
  <p>The mission of the Calvary Internet Ministry extends the Calvary
  Chapel Austin mission statement to the internet:</p>
  <subheading>Win</subheading>
  <p>Reach the lost by presenting the gospel using interesting
  technologies, such as RealAudio, RealVideo, Flash, discussion
  forums, and others.</p>
  <p>Introduce the church and the Calvary Chapel Movement for those
  moving or searching for a church home</p>
  <subheading>Equip</subheading>
  <p>Communicate events/news with the body</p>
  <p>Present transcripts and audio/video archives of services for
  further study</p>
  <subheading>Send</subheading>
  <p>Enabling the body to utilize their spiritual gifts electronically
  to become virtual missionaries</p>
</content>
